author: Melinda Nicholson
content: Hired a hot tub a few weeks ago, Top quality service. Had a problem rang the out of hours line and the kind young lad was here within 20 mins and that was at 7pm. Was abit wary due to the current situation but both lads wore masks the whole time and put my mind at ease. Only problem i have is that there fully booked over Christmas and new year ğŸ˜
